Happy Certified Nursing Assistants Week! 🎉

We want to recognize and celebrate the dedication, compassion, and hard work it takes to be a CNA.

To show our appreciation, this CNA Week, we’re excited to announce a special giveaway!

We are giving away 50 pairs of @weargales Frontline shoes to 50 lucky CNAs! ✨

To enter the giveaway:

1️⃣ Follow @connectRNapp 
2️⃣ Like this post
3️⃣ Tag a CNA friend who deserves a comfortable pair of Gales shoes in the comments (so you both can enter to win a pair!)

Each tagged friend counts as an additional entry, so don’t forget to tag all the deserving CNAs in your life!

Thank you to all the CNAs in our community for your unwavering dedication and commitment to patient care. We are grateful for everything you do. Good luck!⁣ 🎉👟

Winners will be announced on 6/20 at 10 am ET via an update to this post and a direct message from connectRN’s official Instagram page.

Winners must be located in the United States and must be 18 years or older at the time of entry. This contest is not affiliated with Instagram or Facebook. By participating or entering, you agree to release Instagram of all liability.
